oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Duncan's Grocery
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of people inside Duncan's Grocery store in Williamsport, Tennessee. Mars candy bars and other merchandise can be seen on and hanging above the counters. A man (on right) leans against a scale in the foreground. Handwriting on the bottom left corner of the photograph reads "Jan 1972."
